    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't focused on cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the passenger door, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has plenty of life left if you don't mind the visual wear.",
