    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver. While the exterior looks great from a distance, a closer look will reveal some minor road rash on the front bumper and a few small door dings. The interior is clean and free of tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles.",
